stories.text:
When I was starting out it was hard to figure out what was the best direction to go in tech. There are so many specialisations and niches and getting in contact with people is hard.

We built Casa (trycasa.app) as a place to get in contact with those that seem unreachable.

My colleague Dhruv (trycasa.app/dhruv) who has 10+ years in PM in the valley is using the platform to give free group sessions to anyone that requests time.

Join the free group session on "Breaking into Product Management" here: https://trycasa.app/e/gXxLdYR68ZsSYNMg0yTj

Join a group session with him if you're new to tech and want advice on where to start, how to start, or just want an outside perspective on your current path!
